THANKS: Acknowledgements for help with the ed line editor.

Last modified: 2011-04-14 <alm@slewsys.org>

* CSRG
Ed was originally written and released as part of a whirlwind
effort to complete the first public release of CSRG's BSD Unix.

* Algorithm
The editor algorithm is from Brian W. Kernighan & P. J. Plauger's
wonderful book "Software Tools in Pascal," Addison-Wesley, 1981.

